[ctns_make id='axClosedS2']

    [ctns_backspeak]
A set F is closed under addition if the sum of x plus y is both unique and a member of F for values x and y in F, 
    [/ctns_backspeak]

    [ctns_front]
Field Axioms<br/><br/>Closure Under Addition
    [/ctns_front]
        
    [ctns_back style='width:70%;']
A set $$\mathbb{F}$$ is <strong>closed under addition</strong> if 
<br/><br/>$$x+y \in \mathbb{F}$$ and $$x+y$$ is unique<br/><br/>for $$x, y \in \mathbb{F}$$.
    [/ctns_back]
    
[/ctns_make]
